== Teamboard

Quick&dirty implementation of dashboard for Bugzilla 3.6+

Features:

* Independent from Bugzilla database with auto synchronization [not cron]
* Collect and show charts of statistical data 
* Sprint and release dashboards
* Admin UI

Dependencies:

* Rails 3.1
* gem rails_admin for admin interface
* gem devise for user management
* gem bootstrap-sass [for Twitter's bootstrap css framework]
* jQuery, jQuery UI, jQuery data_table